- > 任务要求参赛者根据论文中对某项科研工作的描述，从论文库中找出与该描述最匹配的 Top3 论文。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%8F%82%E8%B5%9B%E8%80%85%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%B9%E6%9F%90%E9%A1%B9%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%87%E5%BA%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8E%E8%AF%A5%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0%E6%9C%80%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E7%9A%84%20Top3%20%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%87%E3%80%82))

- > 该任务是经典的检索排序任务，即根据文本 Query 从候选 Documents 中找出 Top N 个最相关的 Documents，核心技术包括文本语义理解和搜索排序。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E8%AF%A5%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%20Query%20%E4%BB%8E%E5%80%99%E9%80%89%20Documents%20%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA%20Top%20N%20%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%80%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%9A%84%20Documents%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%92%8C%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E3%80%82))

- > 评测使用的评价指标为 Mean Average Precision @3 (MAP@3)  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E8%AF%84%E6%B5%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E4%B8%BA%20Mean%20Average%20Precision%20@3%20(MAP@3)))

- > 综合考量方案的效率和精准性后，本次评测中使用的算法架构包括 “检索召回” 和“精准排序”两个阶段。其中，检索召回阶段负责从候选集中高效快速地召回候选 Documents，从而缩减问题规模，降低排序阶段的复杂度，此阶段注重召回算法的效率和召回率；精准排序阶段负责对召回数据进行重排序，采用 Learning to Rank 相关策略进行排序最优解求解。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E8%80%83%E9%87%8F%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E5%92%8C%E7%B2%BE%E5%87%86%E6%80%A7%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%AC%E6%AC%A1%E8%AF%84%E6%B5%8B%E4%B8%AD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%20%E2%80%9C%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E2%80%9D%20%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E7%B2%BE%E5%87%86%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%8E%E5%80%99%E9%80%89%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%99%E9%80%89%20Documents%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E7%BC%A9%E5%87%8F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A4%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E7%8E%87%EF%BC%9B%E7%B2%BE%E5%87%86%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E5%AF%B9%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E9%87%8D%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%20Learning%20to%20Rank%20%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E6%9C%80%E4%BC%98%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%82%E8%A7%A3%E3%80%82))

- > 召回阶段的方案需要权衡召回覆盖率和算法效率两个指标，一方面召回覆盖率决定了后续精排算法的效果上限，另一方面单纯追求覆盖率而忽视算法效率则不能满足评测时效性的要求。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%9D%83%E8%A1%A1%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E7%8E%87%E5%92%8C%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E7%8E%87%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%AD%E7%B2%BE%E6%8E%92%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%8D%95%E7%BA%AF%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E7%8E%87%E8%80%8C%E5%BF%BD%E8%A7%86%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E5%88%99%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E8%AF%84%E6%B5%8B%E6%97%B6%E6%95%88%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82))

- > 比赛过程中对比实验了两种召回方案，基于 “文本语义向量表征“和“基于空间向量模型 + Bag-of-Ngram”。由于本任务文本普遍较长且专有名词较多等数据特点，实验表明“基于空间向量模型 + Bag-of-Ngram” 的召回方案效果更好  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E6%AF%94%E8%B5%9B%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%20%E2%80%9C%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E8%A1%A8%E5%BE%81%E2%80%9C%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%20+%20Bag-of-Ngram%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E6%9C%AC%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%99%AE%E9%81%8D%E8%BE%83%E9%95%BF%E4%B8%94%E4%B8%93%E6%9C%89%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%9A%E7%AD%89%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%20+%20Bag-of-Ngram%E2%80%9D%20%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD))

- > 可以看到相比于传统的 BM25 和 TFIDF 等算法，F1EXP、F2EXP 等公理检索模型（Axiomatic Retrieval Models）可以取得更高的召回覆盖率，该类模型增加了一些公理约束条件，例如基本术语频率约束，术语区分约束和文档长度归一化约束等等。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%8E%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%20BM25%20%E5%92%8C%20TFIDF%20%E7%AD%89%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8CF1EXP%E3%80%81F2EXP%20%E7%AD%89%E5%85%AC%E7%90%86%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%88Axiomatic%20Retrieval%20Models%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E6%9B%B4%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E7%8E%87%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%A5%E7%B1%BB%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%85%AC%E7%90%86%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%AF%E8%AF%AD%E9%A2%91%E7%8E%87%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%AF%E8%AF%AD%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F%E5%92%8C%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E5%BD%92%E4%B8%80%E5%8C%96%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F%E7%AD%89%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82))

- > 为了提升召回算法的效果，我们使用倒排索引技术对数据进行建模，然后在此基础上实现了 F1EXP、DFR、F2EXP、BM25、TFIDF 等多种检索算法，极大了提升了召回部分的运行效率。为了平衡召回率和计算成本，最后使用 F1EXP、BM25、TFIDF 3 种算法各召回 50 条结果融合作为后续精排候选数据，在验证集上测试，召回覆盖率可以到 70%。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%80%92%E6%8E%92%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%AF%B9%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%BB%BA%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E5%9C%A8%E6%AD%A4%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%20F1EXP%E3%80%81DFR%E3%80%81F2EXP%E3%80%81BM25%E3%80%81TFIDF%20%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E6%A3%80%E7%B4%A2%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E6%9E%81%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%86%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E4%BA%86%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%E3%80%82%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E7%8E%87%E5%92%8C%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20F1EXP%E3%80%81BM25%E3%80%81TFIDF%203%20%E7%A7%8D%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%90%84%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%2050%20%E6%9D%A1%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E8%9E%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%AD%E7%B2%BE%E6%8E%92%E5%80%99%E9%80%89%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E7%8E%87%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%88%B0%2070%25%E3%80%82))

- > 原始 BERT 使用 Pointwise 模式把排序问题看做单文档分类问题，Pointwise 优化的目标是单条 Query 与 Document 之间的相关性，即回归的目标是 label。而 Pairwise 方法的优化目标是两个候选文档之间的排序位次（匹配程度），更适合排序任务的场景。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%20BERT%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20Pointwise%20%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%8A%8A%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9C%8B%E5%81%9A%E5%8D%95%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8CPointwise%20%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%95%E6%9D%A1%20Query%20%E4%B8%8E%20Document%20%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%9B%9E%E5%BD%92%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%20label%E3%80%82%E8%80%8C%20Pairwise%20%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%80%99%E9%80%89%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E4%BD%8D%E6%AC%A1%EF%BC%88%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B4%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF%E3%80%82))

- > 改进模型优化目标：Pointwise 模式下模型使用的 Cross Entropy Loss 作为损失函数，优化目标是提升分类效果，而 Pairwise 模式下模型使用 Hing Loss 作为损失函数，优化目标是加大正例和负例在语义空间的区分度。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9B%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%9APointwise%20%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%20Cross%20Entropy%20Loss%20%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E6%8D%9F%E5%A4%B1%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%20Pairwise%20%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20Hing%20Loss%20%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E6%8D%9F%E5%A4%B1%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%AD%A3%E4%BE%8B%E5%92%8C%E8%B4%9F%E4%BE%8B%E5%9C%A8%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82))

- > LightGBM 在传统的 GBDT 基础上有如下创新和改进：

采用 Gradient-based One-Side Sampling(GOSS) 技术去掉很大部分梯度很小的数据，只使用剩下的去估计信息增益，避免低梯度长尾部分的影响；

采用 Exclusive Feature Bundling(EFB) 技术以减少特征的数量；

传统 GBDT 算法最耗时的步骤是使用 Pre-Sorted 方式找到最优划分点，其会在排好序的特征值上枚举所有可能的特征点，而 LightGBM 中会使用 histogram 算法替换了 GBDT 传统的 Pre-Sorted，牺牲一定精度换取了速度。

LightGBM 采用 Leaf-Wise 生长策略，每次从当前所有叶子中找到分裂增益最大的一个叶子，然后分裂，如此循环。因此同 Level-Wise 相比，在分裂次数相同的情况下，Leaf-Wise 可以降低更多的误差，得到更好的精度。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=LightGBM%20%E5%9C%A8%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%20GBDT%20%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E5%92%8C%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9B%EF%BC%9A%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%20Gradient-based%20One-Side%20Sampling(GOSS)%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%8E%BB%E6%8E%89%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%A2%AF%E5%BA%A6%E5%BE%88%E5%B0%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%89%A9%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%BB%E4%BC%B0%E8%AE%A1%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%A2%9E%E7%9B%8A%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%BD%8E%E6%A2%AF%E5%BA%A6%E9%95%BF%E5%B0%BE%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%9B%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%20Exclusive%20Feature%20Bundling(EFB)%20%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%9B%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%20GBDT%20%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%80%E8%80%97%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20Pre-Sorted%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%80%E4%BC%98%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E6%8E%92%E5%A5%BD%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%9A%E4%B8%BE%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%20LightGBM%20%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20histogram%20%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2%E4%BA%86%20GBDT%20%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%20Pre-Sorted%EF%BC%8C%E7%89%BA%E7%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A6%E6%8D%A2%E5%8F%96%E4%BA%86%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82LightGBM%20%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%20Leaf-Wise%20%E7%94%9F%E9%95%BF%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1%E4%BB%8E%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%B6%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E5%A2%9E%E7%9B%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%B6%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%AD%A4%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E3%80%82%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E5%90%8C%20Level-Wise%20%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B0%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8CLeaf-Wise%20%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%AF%E5%B7%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82))

- > 基于 Light GBM 的方案需要特征工程的配合。在我们实践中，特征主要包括 Statistic Semantic Features（包括 F1EXP、F2EXP、TFIDF、BM25 等）、Distributed Semantic Features（包括 Glove、Doc2vec 等）和 Ranking Features（召回阶段的排序序列特征），并且这些特征分别从标题、摘要、关键词等多个维度进行抽取，最终构建成特征集合，配合 LightGBM 的 pairwise 模式进行训练。  ([🌐 摘要链接](https://tech.meituan.com/2020/03/26/wsdm-2020-bert-lightgbm.html#js_content:~:text=%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%20Light%20GBM%20%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%20Statistic%20Semantic%20Features%EF%BC%88%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%20F1EXP%E3%80%81F2EXP%E3%80%81TFIDF%E3%80%81BM25%20%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81Distributed%20Semantic%20Features%EF%BC%88%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%20Glove%E3%80%81Doc2vec%20%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%20Ranking%20Features%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%AC%E5%9B%9E%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%97%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E4%BB%8E%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E3%80%81%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81%E3%80%81%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E8%AF%8D%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%B4%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8A%BD%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%90%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%20LightGBM%20%E7%9A%84%20pairwise%20%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83%E3%80%82))
